# SEO Rules

## Metadata
- Every page exports `generateMetadata` (or static `metadata`) using the shared `buildMetadata({ title, description, path })` helper in `lib/metadata.ts`.
- Titles < 60 chars, descriptions < 155 chars.
- Set canonical URLs from `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL`.

## Open Graph
- Per-page OG title/description + OG image.
- `twitter:card = summary_large_image`.

## Structured data (JSON-LD)
- `Organization` schema in root layout (name: MTX Hosting, parent: MTX Studio, areaServed: EU).
- `Product` + `Offer` schema on `/plans` and service detail pages, prices from `lib/plans.ts`.

## Files
- `sitemap.ts` lists all public routes.
- `robots.ts` allows all, points to sitemap.

## Target terms (weave naturally, no stuffing)
- "managed WordPress hosting EU"
- "managed Next.js hosting"
- "managed hosting UK"
- "EU web hosting with support"

## Rules
- Real `<h1>` once per page, logical heading order.
- Descriptive link text, no "click here".
- Image `alt` text describes content, not keywords.
